{"tid":190674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杭州單戀男表白被打槍　竟把高中女同學抬起丟下陽台","createTime":"2017-04-07T09:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T09:47:38.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d21c37cb15e20a355a4e5958b54f6c03bc364c65","tid":190674,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>杭州單戀男表白被打槍　竟把高中女同學抬起丟下陽台</strong><br />\n<br />\n浙江省杭州市一名薛姓男子向單戀多時的高中女同學告白，但卻被當面拒絕，他一怒之下竟將對方從陽台推下，導致女同學墜樓身亡。日前薛男已被逮捕，但檢方並未透露其年齡細節。<br />\n<br />\n杭州市檢察院表示，薛男和王女是高中同學，兩人在濱江區合租一屋。3月21日上午，單戀已久的薛男向王女告白，沒想到被直接拒絕，他羞憤之餘，竟闖入房間，將王女推至陽台欄杆處，並把王女整個人抬起來丟下陽台，害王女墜樓，多處器官損傷身亡。<br />\n<br />\n杭州市人民檢察院近日以涉嫌故意殺人罪，將犯罪嫌疑人薛男批准逮捕。"},{"pid":"c5371e946737822086b24e3a5b2c4bf60a7d6d89","tid":190674,"uid":47586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"Dom條女落街"},{"pid":"c76648734f729b825c1ca7c4d7019d07ebbce748","tid":190674,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個誤會個標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc8e86af6052b846049a7a83df160fe3eac609f","tid":190674,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"強國語文倒退止唔止一百年？"},{"pid":"5a400ebef00e30eef753b07dce248d2fc467f8ae","tid":190674,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec487372ad2123f74591fca662ee4dc02b80be7","tid":190674,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"住埋同一間屋都埋唔到身, 又真係幾奇怪"},{"pid":"299c46c9415fe79c193b1cba39caf9c3a1e0b9f9","tid":190674,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"